column2: Slidebars is a jQuery Framework for Off-Canvas Menus and Sidebars into your website or web app.

column5:
Method Name Changes

Changed .update() method name to .modify(). Changed a few array
settings on .get() method.

Comments

Added comments on work to be completed on .update() method.

Improved .close()

Improved the .close() method for when no is provided.

Shift Animation

Added shift animation, it’s somewhere between reveal and push.

2.0 Beta 13

Create new extended version of Slidebars with .get() .create()
.destroy() .update() methods for advanced usage and extending the
framework

2.0 Beta 12

Added automatic window resize events to reset css
Improved Support for Custom Transition Durations

Updated dev

Remove transition ends for more stable timings when switching between
open Slidebars.

2.0 Beta 9

Added args shifts for callbacks

Removed *

Unnecessary as this element shouldn’t have any other parameters

Added lite version

Lite version can be used if you don’t need to create or destroy
Slidebars on the fly
Moved MIT license for older versions

2.0 Beta 5

Improved .active callback, removed a few old css styles, improved
safety of open method.

Version 2.0 Beta 4

Events now fire back the controller.

Event changes and jQuery 2.* support

All events now fire on the document, remove a few for in loops which
enables jQuery 2.* support

Version 2.0 Beta 1

Complete overhaul, first beta :)

Removed events from Slidebar elements

Unnecessary

Added events to elements

Open and close events now fire on elements as well and controller

Added registerSlidebar and open/close checks

Now checks to see if another Slidebar is open before opening the
current one.

Added init security check

Can’t call methods without initiating Slidebars first

Placed animation end types in variable

Reduced size by placing animation end types in variable

Improved toggle callback

Toggle callback now fires after animation

Close CSS tweak

Hide closed Slidebars

Relocated create and destroy callbacks and events

Relocated create and destroy callbacks and events

Improved closed function

Throws an error if an incorrect id was passed

Rework animation, open and close

Reworked the entire animation, open and close methods. Callbacks on
these now run after animation has completed

Removed shift references

Remove shift animation style for now, this will need some more attention

Active method improved

Calling active method without supplying an id will return id of any
active Slidebar

Improved destroy method

Closed Slidebar if open and trigger event before removal

A functioning version with events

Cleaned up code added events, still need a lot of work but getting
there.

Updated dev

Added close any slidebars function, changed some variables to private,
added callbacks

Animate, open and close methods started

Just about got some sort of functionality
Fixed offset scope in dev js

Updated dev version

Added CSS setup

Updated dev version

Added a load of security checks and active method

Updated dev version

Added create and destroy methods

Updated dev version

Created initiation method, started on a few functions.

Updated dev JS

Loops through each of the off canvas elements adding them to a object.

Updated dev css

Added animation styles, widths and heights, print styles and animation.

Updated dev version

Markup planning and basic css

Clean Up

Getting ready for the next dev version.

Updated 0.10.3 beta

Fixes an issue with jQuery .animate animation method

Updated dev version to 0.10.3

Changed min-height for site container calculation, added a clearfix for
the site container, improved iOS support, rewrote close control class
clicks and added link targets.

Updated dev

Changed user event handlers to on body, added a version console log api
method.

Updated dev version

Further development on web app setting. New site min-height
calculations with vh use and js fallback. Only animation inline styling
removed on close as opposed to all. Targets in links now followed when
closing a Slidebar.

Development started for 0.11

Added callback functions, and web app class.

Updated dev version

Fixes issues with scrolling Slidebars and links.

Updated dev version

Removed touchend events for links in Slidebars to fix scrolling bug.

Update dev version

Changed class .sb-lock to .sb-scroll-lock, and option siteLock to
scrollLock.

Updated development version

Fixes a bug with Android opening animation

Merge pull request #56 from mscdex/patch-1

fix typo in readme

Bug fixes

Fixes an issue with push/overlay styles and custom widths.

0.9.4

Fixes an issue with site locking and scrolling difficulty.

0.9.3

jQuery plugin registry and Bower support

Merge pull request #6 from wibimaster/Fix_Undefined_Object

Fix undefined object.

Version 0.7.1

• Added Slidebars options.
• Added helper class html.sb-android for Android Browser version 2.*.
Can be used to unfix your elements with position fixed.
• Added helper class .sb-disable-close. Apply to a link in a Slidebar
to prevent it from closing on click.
• Smoother jQuery .animate() animations on window resize events.
• Cleaned up code.
